            <title>[SPARK-17928] No driver.memoryOverhead setting for mesos cluster mode</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SPARK-17928</link>
                <project id="12315420" key="SPARK">Spark</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Mesos cluster mode does not have a configuration setting for the driver&apos;s memory overhead. This makes scheduling long running drivers on mesos using dispatcher very unreliable. There is an equivalent setting for yarn-- spark.yarn.driver.memoryOverhead.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
